elements.name: Home page is displayed once set credential in login page

steps.name: 'PHP travel' page is loaded
set my credentials on 'Login' page
click on tours menu
go to the tours page
click on add button on Tours page
select "Enabled" Status on Add Tours page
fill "Bolivia" Name field on Add Tours page
fill "2" Quantity Adults field on Add Tours page
fill "260" Price Adults field on Add Tours page
select "3" Stars on Add Tours page
fill "3" Total Days field on Add Tours page
fill "2" Total Nights field on Add Tours page
select "Adventure" Tour Type on Add Tours page
select "Yes" Feature on Add Tours page
select "La Paz" Location 1 on Add Tours page
